# Large Wave Execution Flow

- Run an `explore` sub-agent before implementation to confirm scope and dependencies.
- Implement in two steps:
  - Step A: usable end-to-end feature path.
  - Step B: hardening (i18n, edge cases, guard behavior, docs).
- Run a `code-reviewer` sub-agent after implementation.
- Fix all critical/high findings before marking done.
- Run `npm run verify` and record evidence in verification docs.

## Definition of Done

- In-scope routes/features implemented.
- Sub-agent review completed.
- Verification gates passing.
- Verification artifact updated with pass/fail notes.
